Package com.azure.spring.integration.core.implementation.instrumentation

Class AbstractProcessorInstrumentation<T>

java.lang.Object
com.azure.spring.integration.core.implementation.instrumentation.AbstractProcessorInstrumentation<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Instrumentation
Direct Known Subclasses:
EventHubsProcessorInstrumentation, ServiceBusProcessorInstrumentation
public abstract class AbstractProcessorInstrumentation<T> extends Object implements Instrumentation
Abstract instrumentation class for a messaging processor client. Because a process is self-recoverable, so the instrumentation will mark the processor as UP if no exceptions happen in a time window after marking it as DOWN.
